Package: healthburdenr
Title: Interactive Dashboard Comparing the Estimation of Burden of Healthcare-Associated Infections in Germany and European Union
Version: 1.0.0.0000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jay Ashok", "Chauhan", , "jcha0338@student.monash.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools and interactive visualizations for exploring 
    healthcare-associated infection (HAI) burden estimates based on point 
    prevalence survey data from European acute-care hospitals (2011-2012). 
    Includes population estimates, stratified analyses, and disability-adjusted 
    life years (DALYs) calculations. Based on Zacher et al.(2019). 
